00:03:05.580 --> 00:03:10.740
I'm in the minus. I'm a bit on the thinner side, but well within that 5kg.

00:03:10.740 --> 00:03:15.040
It's not like I'm just barely within 5kg of that ideal spot.

00:03:15.380 --> 00:03:18.300
I want to put on weight in the right places.

00:03:18.300 --> 00:03:25.360
The way it is now is... It can't be helped, I just want what I can't have.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:26.660
I'm hungry.

00:03:26.660 --> 00:03:29.060
If I eat a little bit, I get really hungry.

00:03:29.060 --> 00:03:31.060
If I eat a just a little,

00:03:31.060 --> 00:03:33.500
my stomach balloons up again.

00:03:33.500 --> 00:03:38.420
It's no fun, but eating nothing at all is the most bearable.

00:03:38.720 --> 00:03:44.380
My stomach gets small and enters hibernation mode, so that's the most bearable.

